{"id":324153,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/11/【图说天朝】常德接访官员摆造型与绝症访民/","date":"2013-11-30T14:52:18Z","modified":"2013-11-30T14:52:18Z","title":"【图说天朝】常德接访官员摆造型与“绝症”访民微笑合影留念","content":"<p>2013年11月18日，湖南省常德市临澧县派官员前往省城长沙接访，期间，官员摆姿势与身患“癌症”的访民段新德合影留念。</p>\n<p>几年前，段新德被临澧县自来水公司有关人员打成轻伤。尽管当地启动司法程序，但效果并非明显，就连医药费也未得到赔偿。段新德多次在各级官员经过地喊冤求助，但每次都被信访部门接回。段新德已身患“绝症”一年多，他迫切希望政法部门在他临死前了结此案，否则他将会死不瞑目。</p>\n<p>今年八月，临澧县信访局有官员在接访时，曾为段新德摇扇哄其回家。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/11/20131118_828acbb529f23b1ab196F3Nhwi15DnAM.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-324154\" alt=\"20131118_828acbb529f23b1ab196F3Nhwi15DnAM\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/11/20131118_828acbb529f23b1ab196F3Nhwi15DnAM.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"398\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/11/20131118_828acbb529f23b1ab196F3Nhwi15DnAM.jpg 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/11/20131118_828acbb529f23b1ab196F3Nhwi15DnAM-300x199.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><br />\n常德接访官员摆酷与“绝症”访民合影留念<br />\n<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/11/20131118_b4d42926016f7697022bLi9egrAFcW19.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-324155\" alt=\"20131118_b4d42926016f7697022bLi9egrAFcW19\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/11/20131118_b4d42926016f7697022bLi9egrAFcW19.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"401\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/11/20131118_b4d42926016f7697022bLi9egrAFcW19.jpg 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/11/20131118_b4d42926016f7697022bLi9egrAFcW19-300x200.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/11/20131118_eeb3676715c7e683b6e4wP48awSfJxYf.jpg\"><img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-324156\" alt=\"20131118_eeb3676715c7e683b6e4wP48awSfJxYf\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/11/20131118_eeb3676715c7e683b6e4wP48awSfJxYf.jpg\" width=\"600\" height=\"399\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/11/20131118_eeb3676715c7e683b6e4wP48awSfJxYf.jpg 600w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2013/11/20131118_eeb3676715c7e683b6e4wP48awSfJxYf-300x199.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><br />\n临澧县信访局有官员在接访时，曾为段新德摇扇哄其回家</p>\n","author":980,"categories":[18270,18269,10466,21627],"tags":[22544,9085,17930,15218]}